{"tid":431233,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"去旅行， 手機定舊DC邊樣好？","createTime":"2017-10-10T13:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T05:33:01.000Z","uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5115a29d62454143be93d36e0ac5c8da353d6f5","tid":431233,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:35:46.000Z","msg":"黎緊11 月想去旅行。<br />\n一直都係帶部好舊既dc仔(fujifilm x10) <br />\n但今次想唔帶， 用電話算<br />\n如果同note8/v30/u11 比<br />\n其實同x10 差幾遠？<br />\n因為其實都幾重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b33b2aa75faedcc577d6f047d52ea7685bbd3c7","tid":431233,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T17:16:23.000Z","msg":"你既然2部機都有, 點解唔自己試下呢?<br />\n日光我諗都有乜好比. <br />\n影下夜景先見真章"},{"pid":"77b69771390fc13c0fff8b7d42d285cca4c43e9d","tid":431233,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T07:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你既然2部機都有, 點解唔自己試下呢?<br />\n日光我諗都有乜好比. <br />\n影下夜景先見真章</blockquote><br />\n因為唔識試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249f3aafa04bd1a967a0b02d3c6e887240bed141","tid":431233,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T18:37:42.000Z","msg":"日光可能電話影仲靚<br />\n但電話較唔到shutter speed（車軌長曝腳架夜景）、星芒<br />\n<br />\n我都有部X10不過粒電死左<br />\n有得zoom先係佢同電話最大既分別<br />\n同埋富士色可以執少d相"},{"pid":"f9b2aacfb3ea15bbf45e0b1b35fb09ee5ffb4841","tid":431233,"uid":53748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T18:54:20.000Z","msg":"fujifilm x10 用咗應該有六年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家去旅行都係用緊佢<br />\n我覺得呢部影相都仲好okay<br />\n係有時會想買部輕啲咁，成日覺得佢好重<br />\n但係個鏡頭有粒黑點，唔知拎唔拎去整好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595d925df0fe1d9fcae273edbc1d8fa0cf1beee1","tid":431233,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:31:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fujifilm x10 用咗應該有六年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家去旅行都係用緊佢<br />\n我覺得呢部影相都仲好okay<br />\n係有時會想買部輕啲咁，成日覺得佢好重<br />\n但係個鏡頭有粒黑點，唔知拎唔拎去整好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前貪佢個樣復古，影相又ok就買左<br />\n而家覺得鏡頭突出黎唔方便又比同期dc重<br />\n<br />\n因為準備換電話所以諗緊下次旅行仲帶唔帶好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家睇中g6/v30 因爲有wide 鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7d2eddafe38fc9ae4d55f767a8f8e246c05b46","tid":431233,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb7b7b6d230910e6c913131782430b77b204a0c","tid":431233,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}